{"tid":1886022,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃藍Youtube資料庫第二輪：推廣黃色Youtuber","createTime":"2020-02-18T16:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T13:53:47.000Z","uid":107092,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d9be047406846ba5c3a51f2d68763493eab917","tid":1886022,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"Youtube嘅演算法只會推薦你睇開嘅類型，<br />\n令平時接觸到嘅Channel受限，<br />\n所以我決定開個IG帳號嚟推廣不同類型嘅影片比大家，<br />\n等大家可以接觸到多啲唔同類型嘅影片，<br />\n認識更多Channel。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但由於IG不能夠直接貼Link比大家，<br />\nFacebook又卡住係驗證度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我開設咗個只更新播放清單嘅Youtube Channel，<br />\n將介紹過嘅片更新落播放清單度，<br />\n方便各位查看，<br />\n驗證完咗都會設置埋Facebook Page直接些牙比大家。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1LzyLODPzMf92khtjFRIoA/playlists?view_as=subscriber\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC1LzyLODPzMf92khtjFRIoA%2Fplaylists%3Fview_as%3Dsubscriber&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b813d04f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1LzyLODPzMf92khtjFRIoA/playlists?view_as=subscriber</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/?hl=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellowyoutubehk%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-tw&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=8c096ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/?hl=zh-tw</a>"},{"pid":"02305139a6fff83c1ecd236c00ed1f097e88882d","tid":1886022,"uid":107092,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"點解XXX係黃？<br />\n係回答之前，<br />\n我想問下有冇藍絲質疑過何志光以前係本土派 / 社民連朋友？<br />\n有冇見過藍絲話KOL100係偽藍？<br />\n佢地冇一個出嚟派口罩嘅時候，<br />\n有冇藍絲嫌佢地做得唔夠多？<br />\n<br />\n一個Youtuber一旦公開、明顯地表態，<br />\n即使佢幾偽黃依然會被藍 / 紅嘅公司封殺。<br />\n當然啦，用光環嚟呃錢食女另計，不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n在我嘅角度，同黃色經濟圈一樣，絕對係宜鬆不宜緊。<br />\n因為各位仲可以用自己嘅個人喜好嚟把關，<br />\n你覺得佢偽黃，<br />\n嫌佢做得唔夠多之類嘅你可以唔訂閱佢、唔懲罰佢，<br />\n但佢會係榜上有名。<br />\n而且Youtuber嚟講，<br />\n做藍絲個面係絕對好做過黃好撚多，<br />\n求其拍一條鳩up片都過十萬人睇。<br />\n藍絲係唔屌鳩同路人方面係絕對值得我地學習。"},{"pid":"a1286b53b625687d2f13066bf5ed3712444c4541","tid":1886022,"uid":107092,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"點先幫到啲Youtuber？<br />\n最重要係Engagement，<br />\n姐係Like、Share、Subscribe、Comment，<br />\n另外亦可以儘量唔Skip廣告，<br />\n（利申：有啲廣告真係好撚長，成五分鐘，會skip）"},{"pid":"0c3a75048181c6dac90063d3d25f884fdd928e88","tid":1886022,"uid":107092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"小弟都搵咗啲朋友幫手，<br />\n嚟緊幾日應該會更新曬目前收集到嘅channel<br />\n更新完之後就會全面審視返啲channel<br />\n例如佢地嘅分類、黃嘅理據。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我部分朋友唔係跟得好貼，<br />\n有時候會分錯地方，<br />\n我會儘快更正返，<br />\n都明白有大家對部分頻道爭議好大，<br />\n我會盡力做好佢，<br />\nSorry。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404414263475070e42778fc972dd2b717dda90a2","tid":1886022,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMpJh0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMpJh0b.png&h=f8d9e219&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeZdFdx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeZdFdx.png&h=253a36aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHyRrTA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHyRrTA.png&h=1ab662b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f4f465323f4ae636221fb2c0f2398bd512bff1a","tid":1886022,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬，之前有post 整左個google excel 係咪你作品 ? <br />\n知唔知做咩死左link ?"},{"pid":"5af3a7cc837734486fe2b5a76d83171008522ebd","tid":1886022,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4f465323f4ae636221fb2c0f2398bd512bff1a","tid":1886022,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score